With the suppliers Limited Cover, you are covered for
third party liability. You also have limited damage and

With Premium Cover, you get the benefits of the
suppliers Limited Cover (including cover of third party
liability) plus a protection of your security deposit. If
your car is damaged or stolen, the car hire supplier will
keep the excess to cover the costs, which you can
claim back subject to maximum limits as shown in the
Benefits Table of the policy (see links below). Details
on making a claim will be sent in your confirmation
It covers you for flat tyre and tyre replacement, damage
to mirrors and wheels. It also covers you for
replacement of lost keys and personal possessions if
they get stolen from your car.
This product meets the demands and needs of those
who wish to cover their liability for costs charged by the
car hire company, up to a maximum total policy limit of
3,000, if there is damage to or loss of the vehicle
Please note that your policy documentation can be
provided to you in email and/or by post. By clicking on
Add Premium Cover and providing your email address,
